Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.94,0:01:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我剩下的時間有限
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.14,0:01:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,況且若周圍還出現了敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.58,0:01:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在想我是不是離開這個家 離開阿優 這樣會比較好…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.68,0:01:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿優 我們去約會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.35,0:01:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.46,0:01:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 太好了 約會 約會！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.50,0:02:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,約…約會這種事…連我都沒有主動約過人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.97,0:02:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…麻幌是以女傭身份來家裏幫忙的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.74,0:02:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不可以想歪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.14,0:02:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是這件事是麻幌主動提起的 我也沒有理由拒絕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.71,0:02:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對喔 如果是不久前的麻幌 一定不會說出這種話的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.35,0:02:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是 又好像不全是那個原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.49,0:02:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這到底是怎樣的心情變化啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.86,0:02:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天玩得好開心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.86,0:02:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…我也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.64,0:02:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿優 我好像被海風醺醉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.47,0:02:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你…你沒事吧 麻幌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.88,0:02:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,騙你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.28,0:02:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實我只是想這麼做而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.51,0:02:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻…麻幌？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.55,0:02:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請不要把我當成寡廉鮮恥的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.35,0:02:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 我怎麼會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.62,0:02:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 你覺得我怎麼樣呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.22,0:03:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼樣 那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.16,0:03:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.73,0:03:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請告訴我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.26,0:03:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…我喜歡你 麻幌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.81,0:03:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上就好了 請你等一下喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.41,0:03:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.25,0:03:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟麻幌做這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.38,0:03:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.22,0:03:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.35,0:03:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裏有壞小孩嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.89,0:03:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,違反青少年保護條例
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.99,0:03:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.39,0:03:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.30,0:03:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(76,203)\fs18\fnsimhei\bord0\shad1\1c&Hffffff&\fad(700,700)}第9話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.30,0:03:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(190,233)\fs24\fnsimhei\bord0\shad1\1c&Hffffff&\fad(700,700)}LIMELIGHT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.40,0:03:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叉 叉 圈 叉 圈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.07,0:03:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 早上就這麼熱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.54,0:03:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天玩得太過頭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.95,0:03:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早知道就不要臨時小考了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.65,0:03:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,頭好痛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.52,0:04:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叉 叉 圈 叉 叉 叉 這傢伙…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.56,0:04:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還不乖乖聽話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.46,0:04:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(再加油)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.16,0:04:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.86,0:04:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以毒攻毒 只有繼續喝才能消除宿醉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.87,0:04:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身為能幹的美女教師 不能讓人看到我這般模樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.14,0:04:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但現在是緊急情況 沒辦法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.94,0:04:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今還在說什麼呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.05,0:04:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.35,0:04:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈羅 哈羅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.75,0:04:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.85,0:04:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你…你還真臭屁 竟然有駕照啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.49,0:04:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“臭屁”是多餘的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.26,0:04:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.56,0:04:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這…這輛車一定是租來的吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.67,0:04:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 這是我自己的車 有什麼問題嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.97,0:04:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女傭竟然也有自己的車？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.47,0:04:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這臭丫頭…莫非是個不得了的千金小姐？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.51,0:04:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更不能原諒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.81,0:05:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在我們要去橫濱兜風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.71,0:05:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那邊和阿優開心開心地約會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.35,0:05:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且還是約會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.78,0:05:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那裏玩、吃飯然後再繼續玩…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.66,0:05:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼那麼 拜拜羅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.59,0:05:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻幌 看前面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.13,0:05:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻幌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.63,0:05:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好像有點醉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.33,0:05:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唉呀唉呀 這樣不行喔 不能睡在這種地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.57,0:05:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我們去可以稍作休息的地方吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.01,0:05:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就這麼辦吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.28,0:05:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行 不行 不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.58,0:05:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,單純就是古今中外年輕人最容易受騙的險惡陷阱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.62,0:05:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這個違反卑劣寡廉鮮恥淫行條例的女傭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.96,0:05:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身為一個神職者 我一定要阻止你這邪惡的野心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.26,0:05:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要和那個人喝果汁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.70,0:05:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首先要去哪里好呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.84,0:06:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先去遊樂園走走 餓餓肚子好呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.47,0:06:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是說不考慮先後順序
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.38,0:06:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直接殺到中華街去 吃個過癮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.38,0:06:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種瞬間的快感 或許也不錯喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.28,0:06:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻幌 看前面 前面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.45,0:06:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.72,0:06:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,式條老師？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.55,0:06:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然跟來搗亂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.76,0:06:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我早料到會有這樣的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.86,0:06:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻幌 你想做什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.33,0:06:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 因為很麻煩 所以我想用飛彈把她炸個粉碎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.70,0:06:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…不要那樣 不要那樣做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.50,0:06:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.57,0:06:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 拿20釐米機關槍 把她轟成蜂窩如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.44,0:06:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那也不行 絕對不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.95,0:06:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 特別訂購的71口徑88釐米的加農炮呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.35,0:06:48.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.65,0:06:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿優 你希望我怎麼做呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.89,0:06:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果可以的話 我希望你什麼都不要做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.73,0:06:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真討厭 阿優
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.79,0:07:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對於活生生的人 我不會用這麼激烈的手段啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.83,0:07:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一半是我跟你在開玩笑的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.20,0:07:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻幌真是的 你的玩笑不好笑啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.94,0:07:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,另一半大概是認真的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.41,0:07:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這台車搭載了星型複列28汽缸引擎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.68,0:07:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果追得上 你就追看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.15,0:07:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊…等等 你這傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.52,0:07:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 我們到了喔 阿優
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.49,0:07:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首先要去哪里呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.40,0:07:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你所自豪的車子在性能上似乎沒有多大的差異
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.57,0:07:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的陰謀也到此為止了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.34,0:07:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她的頑強個性 當人類實在太浪費了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.61,0:07:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在我才發現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.08,0:07:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師騎的機車竟然是偉士牌 還蠻有品味的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.15,0:07:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那當然羅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.48,0:07:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以能幹美女教師的品味來說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.82,0:07:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這點事不算什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.76,0:08:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行啦 麻幌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.29,0:08:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.59,0:08:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會將式條老師以外的無辜市民捲進來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.54,0:08:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你誇獎我也沒用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.17,0:08:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.17,0:08:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的輪胎爆胎了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.21,0:08:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.04,0:08:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,0H N0 怎麼會這樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.25,0:08:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣不行喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.85,0:08:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出門前要好好檢查才行喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.35,0:08:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會修
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.89,0:08:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 要從哪邊開始玩呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.33,0:08:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛．
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.20,0:08:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要啦 麻幌進去嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.50,0:08:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿優 其實我瞞著你偷偷在煩惱一些事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.41,0:08:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,流河老師的事嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.85,0:08:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.18,0:09:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,流河老師其實是聖者的機械人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.05,0:09:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他懷疑我在你家幫傭其實是在進行某種作戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.49,0:09:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他不但調查我好像連你身邊的事都作了調查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.53,0:09:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那流河老師怎麼說？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.20,0:09:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天他親自來你家確認 應該已經沒有誤會了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.54,0:09:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.97,0:09:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我已經是引退的身份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.54,0:09:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而阿優則是個極為普通的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.65,0:09:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算再怎麼查 也查不出什麼來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.92,0:09:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是 這樣的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.59,0:09:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說住院的理科老師明天就要回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.39,0:09:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,流河老師回去了啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.93,0:09:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.00,0:09:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 因為我的私事而讓你操心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.27,0:09:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼會是私事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.17,0:09:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.71,0:10:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.48,0:10:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.45,0:10:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明已經到換季的時期了 今天還是這麼熱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.19,0:10:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今年的殘暑太酷熱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.32,0:10:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太天真了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.86,0:10:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就那麼一點意外我才不可能氣餒呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.60,0:10:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 為什麼這麼悶熱啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.13,0:10:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好熱好熱 熱得快死掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.40,0:10:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是小企鵝耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.24,0:10:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來 各位小朋友 這就是小企鵝喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.34,0:10:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼頭 別靠過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.15,0:10:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走開 走開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.65,0:10:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走…走開 還不快給我滾 小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.75,0:10:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小企鵝 招呼呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.26,0:10:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小企鵝死翹翹了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.27,0:10:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.27,0:10:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天氣這麼熱 裏面的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.70,0:11:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 內臟大概精疲力竭了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.81,0:11:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.01,0:11:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當內臟的人還真是辛苦啊
