Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.43,0:11:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好看嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.70,0:11:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.11,0:11:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您要買嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.04,0:11:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要買
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.04,0:11:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走 我們去吃飯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.01,0:11:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.08,0:11:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來 阿優 嘴巴張開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.59,0:11:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.89,0:11:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.32,0:11:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 我還是比較喜歡吃你之前作的燒賣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.66,0:11:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真…真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.40,0:12:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真令人嫉妒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.73,0:12:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們買肉包回去當土產吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.74,0:12:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 那請給我那個盒裝的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.24,0:12:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝惠顧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.61,0:12:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小姐 你還沒買單喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.98,0:12:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是是是 買單是嗎 買單
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.48,0:12:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,錢…錢包不見了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.82,0:12:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃霸王餐是重罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.27,0:12:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海邊的風真是舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.35,0:12:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿優 我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.78,0:12:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能夠來阿優家 我真的覺得很幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.79,0:12:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼幸福 太誇張了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.56,0:13:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是麻幌在來我家之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.46,0:13:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,經歷了什麼樣的事 我不太清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.53,0:13:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過我覺得你可以過得比現在更加幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.17,0:13:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 我這樣已經十分幸福了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.01,0:13:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這樣說呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.44,0:13:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為有時候你的表情很悲傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.12,0:13:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是啦 或許是我想太多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.53,0:13:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對…對了 既然特地來這裏我們來拍紀念照吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.10,0:13:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…我去看看附近有沒有在賣相機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.83,0:14:17.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.31,0:14:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是問清楚比較好嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.49,0:14:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻…麻幌 怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.39,0:14:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿優
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.20,0:14:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻…麻幌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.24,0:14:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我失態了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.97,0:14:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自己也不知道該怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.58,0:15:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺到很寂寞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.88,0:15:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以前從未發生過這種事 對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.98,0:15:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天真的很愉快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.19,0:15:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我已經沒事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.90,0:15:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,托你的福 我已經平靜多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.83,0:15:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不需要道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.27,0:15:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才應該道歉 說了奇怪的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.64,0:15:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 阿優什麼錯也沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.91,0:15:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我雖然沒有自信說這種話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.65,0:15:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從我眼中看到的麻幌 幸福還是不幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.72,0:15:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說得再多還是不如麻幌自己感覺到幸福比較重要吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.86,0:15:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是這麼覺得的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.23,0:15:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.40,0:15:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定是這樣子的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.67,0:16:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻…麻幌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.34,0:16:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.54,0:16:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.97,0:16:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果麻幌真的感到自己幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.98,0:16:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請把你遇到的所有事情都說給我聽吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.45,0:16:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.42,0:16:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候都可以 我會等你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.75,0:16:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿優
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.26,0:16:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道周圍的人會是怎麼看我們的喔？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.16,0:16:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿優
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.23,0:16:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個嘛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.67,0:16:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.77,0:16:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該像是那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.10,0:16:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.24,0:16:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐和…弟弟吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.38,0:16:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐和弟弟啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.51,0:16:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那樣也不錯啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.25,0:16:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了 照相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.29,0:16:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道有誰可以幫我們照相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.99,0:16:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家好像都很忙的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.03,0:17:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,式條老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.07,0:17:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.40,0:17:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來得正好 幫我們照相吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.17,0:17:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到我這樣子 你難道不能說些窩心的話給我聽嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.84,0:17:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 偉士牌爆胎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.18,0:17:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在人偶裝裏差點變成即身佛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.85,0:17:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最後還體驗到了中國五千年的恐怖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.12,0:17:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啦好啦 我給你包子吃 請不要這麼氣餒嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.33,0:17:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 老是麻煩你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.40,0:17:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我們先走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.90,0:17:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等 你們要去哪里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.50,0:17:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去哪里 我們只是要回家啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.90,0:17:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你打算拋下我不管嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.81,0:17:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才不管呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.17,0:17:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請靠自己的力量回家吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.94,0:17:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別那麼無情嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.71,0:17:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的車只能坐兩個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.35,0:17:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能想辦法擠擠嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.69,0:17:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小哥 你在這裏做什麼呀？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.82,0:18:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是在偷看啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.09,0:18:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還年輕 去交個女朋友啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.50,0:18:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可能 不可能 他就算再過一百年也交不到啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.54,0:18:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也說句話啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.84,0:18:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿…這傢伙在害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.81,0:18:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我老是被這種人盯上呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.18,0:18:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你找我家的阿優有什麼事嗎 你找我家的美裏同學有什麼事嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.40,0:18:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我們就先告辭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.77,0:18:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,載我回去啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.11,0:18:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿優 其實我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.10,0:19:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是好困喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.50,0:19:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天一整天陪我到處跑 你一定累了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.44,0:19:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會啦 偶而早點睡覺也不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.94,0:19:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請去睡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.85,0:19:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻幌 你還不睡嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.51,0:19:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 不過再一下就可以告一段落了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.69,0:19:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等做好後我再去休息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.52,0:19:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好香啊 肚子好像又餓起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.83,0:19:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以讓我嘗一下味道嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.36,0:19:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唉呀 不行燉湯還得再多煮一會才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.33,0:19:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就期待明天 我先去睡了 晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.14,0:19:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.51,0:20:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.83,0:20:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要走了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.67,0:20:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚聽你那麼一說我才發現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.31,0:20:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我自己的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.94,0:20:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連自己也沒有發現 在不知不覺中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.81,0:20:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我感到自己現在的生活很幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.25,0:20:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻幌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.12,0:20:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要擊倒流河
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.59,0:20:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後一定會再回到這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.36,0:20:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.60,0:20:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.60,0:20:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻幌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.84,0:21:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別使用那個喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.41,0:21:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不打算跟他同歸於盡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.31,0:21:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 不使用那個要如何對抗流河啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.25,0:21:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在的你本來就已經沒什麼勝算了呀
